title: Mike Baird to visit Wendy Whiteley's garden, Sydney's precarious marvel

Wendy Whiteley stepped into her Secret Garden on Friday morning and, not two minutes later, was stopped for a hug. "Bless you, thank you," said Lina Massi, a retired teacher and home gardener from Ashfield.   The Age.
